dservice-2", "checkoutservice-1", "currencyservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "cartservice-2", "frontend-2"]}, "available_metric_names": ["client_error_ratio", "error_ratio", "pod_cpu_usage", "request", "response", "rrt", "rrt_max", "server_error_ratio"], "log_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的日志数据，我现在进行初始扫描分析。从日志中可以看出，主要问题集中在frontend服务无法连接到currency服务。以下是详细分析：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"connection refused\", \"transport is closing\", \"transport\", \"Error while dialing\", \"Unavailable\", \"connection error\", \"failed to convert price\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currency\",\n      \"reason\": \"currency服务出现连接拒绝和传输关闭错误，导致frontend无法获取货币汇率信息\",\n      \"evidence\": \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.39.78:7000: connect: connection refused\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"frontend服务因currency服务不可用导致订单处理失败，无法完成价格转换\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = failed to prepare order: failed to convert price\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析要点总结：**\n\n1. **主要错误模式**：\n   - 连接拒绝错误：`connection refused` 到IP地址 `10.233.39.78:7000`\n   - 传输关闭错误：`transport is closing`\n   - 服务不可用：`Unavailable` 状态码\n\n2. **影响范围**：\n   - 所有frontend实例（frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2）都受到影响\n   - 分布在多个节点（aiops-k8s-01, aiops-k8s-04, aiops-k8s-08）\n\n3. **关键发现**：\n   - 故障表现为currency服务不可用，导致frontend无法获取货币汇率信息\n   - 订单处理失败，无法完成价格转换操作\n   - 错误在故障时间段内持续发生，出现频次较高\n\n这属于典型的服务间连接故障，需要进一步调查currency服务的状态和配置。", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于对故障时间段 2025-06-19T06:10:19Z 到 2025-06-19T06:28:19Z 的追踪数据分析，我已经完成了初始扫描。以下是关键发现：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"currencyservice->frontend\",\n    \"checkoutservice->frontend\",\n    \"frontend->currencyservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->currencyservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\",\n    \"frontend->cartservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"所有frontend节点调用currencyservice均出现connection refused错误，状态码14，连接目标IP 10.233.39.78:7000被拒绝\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"PlaceOrder操作延迟从正常153703ms激增至异常29272ms，延迟倍数约5.3倍，同时出现货币转换失败错误\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice对redis的HGET操作延迟从正常1739ms激增至异常22624ms，延迟倍数约13倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"AddItem和GetCart操作延迟显著增加，从正常2-5秒激增至异常17-33秒，延迟倍数6-10倍\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 分析要点总结：\n\n1. **根因服务**：currencyservice完全不可用，导致所有货币相关操作失败\n2. **传播影响**：currencyservice的故障通过checkoutservice传播到frontend，导致订单处理失败\n3. **性能瓶颈**：redis和cartservice出现严重延迟，进一步加剧了系统性能问题\n4. **错误模式**：连接拒绝错误表明currencyservice可能已宕机或网络隔离\n\n需要进一步分析currencyservice的具体状态以确定根本原因。", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的指标数据，我已经完成了对故障时间段 2025-06-19T06:10:19Z 到 2025-06-19T06:28:19Z 的全面扫描分析。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"rrt_max\", \"rrt\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"request\", \"response\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"shippingservice多个pod出现严重的error_ratio和client_error_ratio异常，故障期间错误率从0%飙升到28.5%-35.63%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"shippingservice-0: error_ratio从0%升至31.66%；shippingservice-1: error_ratio从0%升至28.5%；shippingservice-2: error_ratio从0%升至35.63%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"frontend所有pod均出现server_error_ratio和error_ratio异常，同时rrt_max指标显著下降，表明服务异常导致响应时间异常\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0: server_error_ratio从0%升至40.44%，rrt_max从288863降至34833；frontend-1: server_error_ratio从0%升至41.65%，rrt_max从286205降至34778；frontend-2: server_error_ratio从0%升至40.55%，rrt_max从300389降至35552\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"productcatalogservice-0出现rrt响应时间显著增加，从1315.1ms升至5888.54ms，同时pod_cpu_usage下降表明服务处理能力异常\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt从1315.1ms升至5888.54ms，pod_cpu_usage从0.04降至0.01\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"currencyservice-2出现pod_cpu_usage降为0，同时rrt_max显著下降，表明该pod可能发生重启或异常终止\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage从0.04降至0.0，rrt_max从14360降至4256\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现总结：\n\n1. **shippingservice** 是主要的故障源头，所有3个pod都出现严重的错误率飙升\n2. **frontend服务** 受到连锁影响，出现服务端错误率异常和响应时间异常\n3. **productcatalogservice-0** 出现响应时间显著增加，可能受到上游服务影响\n4. **currencyservice-2** 出现CPU使用率降为0，可能发生pod重启\n\n建议进一步深入分析shippingservice的具体故障原因，以及其对下游服务的影响链。"}
